& [InferenceJobResult] is task-frame routing proposal
  + [task_subject] is summarize SOP source and propose two questions
  + [lane_fit] is lm_studio proposal lane
  + [authority_boundary] is no file edits and Codex owns integration
  + [evidence_gate] is provided SOP text and validator capture
  + [action_gate] is no tools and no repo mutation
  + [outside] is credentials, file edits, and broad authority
  + [next_step] is return proposal for Codex review